lar Does Your Family Actually Need?</h3>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6\">Plug in the typical blackout duration and see which setup makes sense.</p>\n    <solar-sizing products=\"B0D4LMVKYD,B0F4JR1PFM,B0CNPHD4VY,B0BQV4YG1T\" blackoutHours=\"8\" location=\"urban\" />\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- COMPLETE SYSTEMS SECTION -->\n  <section class=\"mb-12\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-raisin dark:text-white mb-4\">Complete Systems (Everything Included)</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6\">For families who don't want to piece things together—or for you if you don't want to explain charge controllers over WhatsApp.</p>\n\n    <!-- Featured Complete System -->\n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 md:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl mb-6 ring-2 ring-lime ring-offset-2 dark:ring-offset-slate-900\">\n      <span class=\"bg-lime text-raisin px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase mb-4 inline-block\">Best Complete System</span>\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6\">\n        <div class=\"w-full md:w-64 shrink-0\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81audnUHPBL._AC_UL320_.jpg\" alt=\"ECO-WORTHY 9.36KWH Complete Solar System\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"rounded-xl w-full h-64 object-contain bg-slate-50\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n          <h3 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-raisin dark:text-white mb-2\" data-asin=\"B0BQV4YG1T\">ECO-WORTHY 9.36KWH 2340W 48V Complete System</h3>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4\">\n            <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold\">4.4★ (445 reviews)</span>\n            <span class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm\">$$$$$ tier</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4\">\n            <strong>VERDICT: The \"never worry about power again\" option.</strong> This is serious infrastructure—12 panels, a 5000W all-in-one inverter, mounting brackets, the works. 9.36KWH of storage means your family can run a fridge, fans, lights, and charge phones through an entire overnight blackout. Plug and play design means minimal installation headaches.\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mb-4\">\n            The reality check: This is heavy, expensive to ship, and requires roof space. Best for families who own their home and have a dedicated installation spot. Not for apartment dwellers.\n          </p>\n          <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BQV4YG1T?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">\n            Check Price on Amazon →\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Starter Kit -->\n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-6\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"w-full sm:w-48 md:w-56 shrink-0\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61yXMVnl07L._AC_UY218_.jpg\" alt=\"Renogy 100W Solar Panel Starter Kit\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-56 object-contain bg-slate-50\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n          <span class=\"bg-sunglow text-raisin px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase mb-2 inline-block\">Best Starter Kit</span>\n          <h3 class=\"text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-raisin dark:text-white mb-2\" data-asin=\"B00BFCNFRM\">Renogy 100W 12V Solar Panel Starter Kit</h3>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\">\n            <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold\">4.6★ (465 reviews)</span>\n            <span class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm